Package: dsmn
Type: Package
Title: Functions for design and monitoring of clinical trials
Version: 0.9-13
Authors@R: c(
  person("Bob", "Gray", email = "gray@jimmy.harvard.edu",
    role = "aut"),
  person("Robert", "Redd", email = "rredd@jimmy.harvard.edu",
    role = "cre")
  )
Author: Bob Gray
Maintainer: Robert Redd <rredd@jimmy.harvard.edu>
Description: Performs various calculations related to design of studies
  with either failure time or binary endpoints, and also functions to
  facilitate monitoring and analysis of such studies, including group
  sequential studies with failure time endpoints and two stage and
  randomized phase II studies.
Imports:
  survival
Suggests:
  knitr,
  rmarkdown,
  testthat
License: GPL-2
LazyData: yes
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
